==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Superfete
<hw>Su`per*fete"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To conceive (another fetus)
after a former conception.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Howell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

